{"tid":2047232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為反共份子,64集會一定要炒起佢","createTime":"2020-06-02T03:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T19:12:50.000Z","uid":53498,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed783ff73a710c5b532ca1636e7729026c71e015","tid":2047232,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"你可以話鄰國關我鳩事？支那有民主仲撚衰<br />\n支聯會永續cap水,出賣港人之類嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n但8964不嬲都係支共其中一個極大嘅罪行,連乜撚賤狼串嘴口交部都極少極少講,64亦係香港言論自由嘅指標之一,勇於表態可以壯大反共聲勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQ8AK9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQ8AK9d.jpg&h=c4945294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af2d68aa453f906ab5542ecaf4e4eaf0bbef0674","tid":2047232,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/05/29/31661/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Farticles%2F2016%2F05%2F29%2F31661%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b89ccfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/05/29/31661/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/03/11/128882/%e5%85%ab%e4%b9%9d%e6%b0%91%e9%81%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%b7%a6%e8%86%a0%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e6%90%9e%e6%95%a3%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F03%2F11%2F128882%2F%25e5%2585%25ab%25e4%25b9%259d%25e6%25b0%2591%25e9%2581%258b%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25b7%25a6%25e8%2586%25a0%25e5%258f%2588%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e6%2590%259e%25e6%2595%25a3%25e9%2581%258b%25e5%258b%2595&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=f6da72f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/03/11/128882/%e5%85%ab%e4%b9%9d%e6%b0%91%e9%81%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%b7%a6%e8%86%a0%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e6%90%9e%e6%95%a3%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95</a><br />\n<br />\n八九民運就係果班大台，升級又唔得，一味用雨革式佔領，到有義士掉毛像，佢地仆街到送佢地去公安，逼到佢地死咁濟。<br />\n<br />\n到開槍清場前，大台果班柒姑碌，自己走左去，由得廣場d人死，升級又左膠當道唔得，撤退又冇時間，老解開槍果陣有d 柒姑碌連d 人還拖都唔俾，最後搞到傷亡慘重。<br />\n<br />\n但係果班領袖走到外國，攞住外國國籍乜都做唔到， 仲話要寬恕中共，做埋無良僱主，痴晒線。"},{"pid":"711770943a8c0dfa78e7bac1af2273df86565fb6","tid":2047232,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2d68aa453f906ab5542ecaf4e4eaf0bbef0674","tid":2047232,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/05/29/31661/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Farticles%2F2016%2F05%2F29%2F31661%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b89ccfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://polymerhk.com/articles/2016/05/29/31661/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/03/11/128882/%e5%85%ab%e4%b9%9d%e6%b0%91%e9%81%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%b7%a6%e8%86%a0%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e6%90%9e%e6%95%a3%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F03%2F11%2F128882%2F%25e5%2585%25ab%25e4%25b9%259d%25e6%25b0%2591%25e9%2581%258b%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25b7%25a6%25e8%2586%25a0%25e5%258f%2588%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e6%2590%259e%25e6%2595%25a3%25e9%2581%258b%25e5%258b%2595&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=f6da72f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/03/11/128882/%e5%85%ab%e4%b9%9d%e6%b0%91%e9%81%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%b7%a6%e8%86%a0%e5%8f%88%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e6%90%9e%e6%95%a3%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95</a><br />\n<br />\n八九民運就係果班大台，升級又唔得，一味用雨革式佔領，到有義士掉毛像，佢地仆街到送佢地去公安，逼到佢地死咁濟。<br />\n<br />\n到開槍清場前，大台果班柒姑碌，自己走左去，由得廣場d人死，升級又左膠當道唔得，撤退又冇時間，老解開槍果陣有d 柒姑碌連d 人還拖都唔俾，最後搞到傷亡慘重。<br />\n<br />\n但係果班領袖走到外國，攞住外國國籍乜都做唔到， 仲話要寬恕中共，做埋無良僱主，痴晒線。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"19年6月前咁樣屌,我無異議,但到今日支共全方位打壓嘅時候,仲要分黨分派係咪自我設限？<br />\n戴耀廷hocc都可以進化嘅時候,點解自己唔行前多一步？<br />\n進化啦香港人"},{"pid":"ff2e4c37d89d73cf03