中國春秋大夢，話自己心中有愧，想中國學香港所以送香港俾中共。<br />\n<br />\n就算發民主中國大夢，只係中華民國係正統，中華人民共和國只係勾結蘇聯既偽政權。<br />\n<br />\n當時冇人趁中共弱勢反對回歸，中共好似弱勢到可以用基本法讓步黎換貸款，如果香港有人食住上反對回歸，香港未必搞到一鑊屎。"},{"pid":"3358a481b42b78c8bab03cfcffe4cb162ab693a0","tid":2047232,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"fad9ca12e97d471c1fd8542ca855a774c7252a6c","tid":2047232,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06bc6321173147421722be00eed7f137924347e","tid":2047232,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:20:29.000Z","msg":"只參加非支聯會及其有關組織舉辦的64活動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6788316df62330d0661f0f7a95281c87675304","tid":2047232,"uid":221211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"Secretary Pompeo<br />\n@SecPompeo<br />\nIt starts; so soon. For the first time in 30 years, Hong Kong authorities denied permission to hold the #TiananmenVigil. If there is any doubt about Beijing&rsquo;s intent, it is to deny Hong Kongers a voice and a choice, making them the same as mainlanders. So much for two systems.<br />\n8:21 PM &middot; Jun 2, 2020&middot;Twitter for iPhone<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1267793562550353923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1267793562550353923&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=ab243829\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1267793562550353923&h=c313eb55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo